details.text: Global interconnect for 2 global loads and 1 global store. Reduce number of global loads and stores to simplify global interconnect.
For 2 global loads and 1 global store.

details.text: This read-only memory contains information for the host about the system and about each kernel in the system, including kernel names, arguments, and attributes.  The system description ROM ensures that the binary image on the FPGA is compatible with the host program.

Additional information.text: Requested size 576 bytes, implemented size 1024 bytes, stall-free, 1 read and 1 write.
Private memory implemented in on-chip block RAM.
Requested size 576 bytes, implemented size 3072 bytes, replicated 3 times total, stall-free, 3 reads and 1 write.
Replicated 3 times to efficiently support multiple accesses. To reduce this replication factor, reduce number of read and write accesses.
Private memory implemented in on-chip block RAM.
Requested size 576 bytes, implemented size 1024 bytes, stallable, 4 reads and 3 writes.

details.text: Reduce the number of write accesses or fix banking to make this memory system stall-free. Banking may be improved by using compile-time known indexing on lowest array dimension.

Additional information.text: Banked on bits 4, 5 into 4 separate banks.
Private memory implemented in on-chip block RAM.
